一个轻量级的jsp mvc, 非常简单，适合小网站。
A simple jsp mvc.  It's so easy and suitable for small website.


在 *.jsp中加入:

<%@ page import="com.github.jsplite.Jsplite" %>
<% Jsplite.inherits("com.xxx.xxx.IndexAction", request, response); %>


在 pom.xml 中加入:

<repositories>
    <repository>
        <id>jsplite-mvn-github</id>
        <url>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lpn520/jsplite/master/mvn-repository</url>
    </repository>
</repositories>

<dependencies>
    <dependency>
        <groupId>com.github</groupId>
        <artifactId>jsplite</artifactId>
        <version>1.0.0</version>
    </dependency>
</dependencies>